{"tid":552152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋民直擊】省鏡師姐 蘇生：揸廿幾年車未見過！","createTime":"2018-02-06T09:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T15:37:12.000Z","uid":36097,"like":9,"dislike":109,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"f20942f11f112a2c10502ee2032627a5db445670","tid":552152,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20131101/large/1383276670_ade9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20131101%2Flarge%2F1383276670_ade9.jpg&h=da8aa158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我揸咗車廿幾年，都未見過咁靚嘅交通督導員！」讀者蘇先生噚日朝早11點幾，為咗幫親友排幼稚園，同唔少家長一齊揸住架車，響九龍塘羅福道附近四圍兜，之後見到兩個交通督導員響度執勤，但視線卻即時被一名年輕師姐吸引住。蘇先生話：「佢睇落應該都係得廿幾歲......好有笑容、好有衝勁，叫啲車走嘅時候都好nice，所以大家(司機)都好合作！」<br />\n<br />\n蘇先生仲話，呢個「比港姐仲靚」嘅交通督導員，就連嚟到幫手維持秩序嘅師兄，都願意主動跨部門向她提供協助。如果大家俾呢位咁靚又有禮貌嘅師姐抄牌，唔知張牛肉乾會唔會食得開心啲呢？"},{"pid":"9a82f7f4753366032fb49cbe61c0e821e837cce0","tid":552152,"uid":36097,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T09:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20131101/large/1383275628_73b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20131101%2Flarge%2F1383275628_73b0.jpg&h=9d0f541e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5451a6728609a5372040d1019086d8662ffc61f8","tid":552152,"uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T09:11:59.000Z","msg":"唔錯啦"},{"pid":"e9e80a7bbf590d9790fe687abdf0c41feb72764e","tid":552152,"uid":45353,"like":32,"dislike":9,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"成個男人都話省鏡"},{"pid":"eb0002444784de3601a245643c509fec2a94d5ad","tid":552152,"uid":26451,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fdda8c599ee9496eea42870ce3419e16171681d","tid":552152,"uid":45772,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0